com.nokia.maps.map

Interface MapSchemeType


  • public interface MapSchemeType
    This interface defines the constants which may be used to set the map provider and are used by the SharingManager and the MapDisplay classes.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int HYBRID
      This constant defines a "Hybrid" map rendering.
      static int NORMAL
      This constant defines a "Normal" map rendering.
      static int SATELLITE
      This constant defines a "Satellite" map rendering.
      static int TERRAIN
      This constant defines a "Terrain" map rendering.
      static int TRANSIT
      This constant defines a "Transit" map rendering.

    • Field Detail
